tevar ( english : attitude ) is a 2015 indian action film directed by amit sharma and written by gunasekhar . the film stars arjun kapoor and sonakshi sinha and in lead roles while manoj bajpayee plays and crucial role . it is an official remake of telugu film okkadu ( 2003 ) . shruti haasan made a special appearance in the song " madamiyan " . the film was released worldwide on 9 january 2015 .